30,"uid":150742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:36:21.000Z","msg":"幫推 其實由好耐之前開始已經冇必要再將勇武同和理非劃開 有好多人都有做唔同ge角色 而兩者都係相輔相成先可以發揮最大功效 我中有你你中有我 只要有共同信念 我地就係同路人 坐埋同一條船我地冇人有資格割蓆 我地之所以行到今日呢一步係因為我地團結呀 一句講晒 永不割蓆 我錫晒你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心想為件事好ge 以後遇到問題唔好只係屌 我地係聰明人 更加重要ge係去諗點樣解決問題 試下多d提出解決問題方法 集思廣益！"},{"pid":"caca8cd3d01b22c1f1ecfb7f67690a4bfcc74988","tid":1418630,"uid":79724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:24:13.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5f9539ef425ae4684c4d7320b477ad65980f6a","tid":1418630,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f062ec72c65f996e135a5c50305d5d4b405e3e","tid":1418630,"uid":163822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:17:24.000Z","msg":"暴力還暴力<br />\n 可唔可以抖返兩日<br />\n我諗啲勇武街坊都要瞓返兩晚"},{"pid":"b9e93f59f95468813d7e838b091020dd9f2d261f","tid":1418630,"uid":69681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:24:48.000Z","msg":"麻煩各位巴絲幫手backup 啲片同相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最好包括直播 記住backup係保障你地 仲有好人好事都可以backup用作宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbackup相： <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf3tObt_TWDBnpJcRWBLYZoiwLBZhEIAWKp7HtFFvTFJPy1lQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSf3tObt_TWDBnpJcRWBLYZoiwLBZhEIAWKp7HtFFvTFJPy1lQ%2Fviewform&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtlT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=40c976e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf3tObt_TWDBnpJcRWBLYZoiwLBZhEIAWKp7HtFFvTFJPy1lQ/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\nbackup片: <a href=\"https: